{
  "id": "69e5f1bb45956620b6d14114",
  "title": "ストレスに対する反応",
  "created": 1776677314,
  "updated": 1776680011,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e5f1bb45956620b6d14114",
      "text": "ストレスに対する反応",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776677314,
      "updated": 1776677314
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5fc070000000000293e44",
      "text": "書いた[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679943,
      "updated": 1776679947
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f21c0000000000e3c77e",
      "text": "ストレス源から離れるタイプ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776677404,
      "updated": 1776677416
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f22a0000000000e3c77f",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/b4ffa0fd1ff0e23602364baf2e742233]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776677419,
      "updated": 1776677736
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f36e0000000000e3c781",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776677742,
      "updated": 1776677745
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f3700000000000e3c782",
      "text": "ストレス源に近づくタイプ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776677745,
      "updated": 1776677755
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f5fc0000000000e3c787",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/0ff4214639ed36a0ea8eeefa1332bdfd]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776678397,
      "updated": 1776678398
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f60a0000000000e3c789",
      "text": " \t↑ 興味で、あるいはストレス源と知らずに近づくタイプ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776678411,
      "updated": 1776678444
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f4370000000000e3c784",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/1aa643730f66e0f67edf827f96dee1e3]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776677943,
      "updated": 1776678341
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f62d0000000000e3c78a",
      "text": " \t↑ ストレス源に立ち向かうタイプ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776678446,
      "updated": 1776678471
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f5c40000000000e3c786",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776678341,
      "updated": 1776678341
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f3670000000000e3c780",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776677736,
      "updated": 1776677736
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f64e0000000000e3c78b",
      "text": "ストレス源が異質なモンスターではなく、同じ人間であり、対等な存在である場合、人間関係の図になる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776678478,
      "updated": 1776678564
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f9600000000000e3c79a",
      "text": " \t互いにストレスを与える存在である前提",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679264,
      "updated": 1776679280
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f6a30000000000e3c78c",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/9c4bfc8596921d15439b83b6eaed9810] [https://gyazo.com/1a0be85171f6e162a0cfbc7d765f7820] [https://gyazo.com/a5e745f4667884c88f9380fba34ee032]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776678564,
      "updated": 1776679123
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5fb080000000000293e3a",
      "text": "  上段左は最も平和的な状況だが、全員が全員このようになっている場合はどこか余所余所しい雰囲気になるかもしれない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679688,
      "updated": 1776679775
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5fb5e0000000000293e3b",
      "text": "  上段中は困るとき",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679775,
      "updated": 1776679825
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5fb750000000000293e3c",
      "text": "  上段右は怖いとき",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679798,
      "updated": 1776679827
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5fba80000000000293e40",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/dfddcf23ac6192f0018cb069fed9a304] [https://gyazo.com/3c372a1f3c3f2374a26b8535a5280b59] [https://gyazo.com/d314dcc733172c44d6abd4224e0e66a1]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679849,
      "updated": 1776679865
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f90c0000000000e3c799",
      "text": "  中段左は上段中の逆",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679180,
      "updated": 1776679890
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5fbc40000000000293e41",
      "text": " \t中段中は良い感じに見えるが、互いがストレスを与える存在であり、互いが興味ないしは無知により近づいているので危ないとも言える",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679877,
      "updated": 1776679877
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5faa60000000000293e39",
      "text": " \t中段右は危ない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679590,
      "updated": 1776679667
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f85f0000000000e3c794",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/98960f6a05aba9d79ee34fa4169311c5] [https://gyazo.com/b4c4d70589db6fc9f114f93d8ea43521] [https://gyazo.com/aafc0c582a4f7da8ca981773be1c5dc3]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679007,
      "updated": 1776679130
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f8a30000000000e3c798",
      "text": "  下段左は上段右の逆",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679075,
      "updated": 1776679909
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5fbe40000000000293e43",
      "text": "  下段中は中段右の逆",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679909,
      "updated": 1776679921
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5fbd90000000000293e42",
      "text": "  下段右が戦争の始まり",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679898,
      "updated": 1776679898
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f2160000000000e3c77d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776677399,
      "updated": 1776679610
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5fc4b0000000000293e47",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776680011,
      "updated": 1776680011
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5fc1f0000000000293e45",
      "text": "[自他境界の図]が頭にある状態で別のことを考えていたら繋がった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679967,
      "updated": 1776680011
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5fc1f0000000000293e46",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776679968,
      "updated": 1776679968
    }
  ]
}